high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the fridge and turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Cut the tomato on the kitchen table into slices.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the left end of the counter.
Place the knife on the counter in front of the toaster.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the microwave above the stove.
Heat the tomato in the microwave and remove it.
Take a step to the left to face the counter.
Place the tomato slice on the counter.
